data.title: What precautions should I take to stay safe during a lake-effect snow warning?
data.meta_description: Answer (1 of 2): Well the precautions are not DURING you must be ready ahead of the event. You should make sure of your energy backups for heating and you should have the tools and etc. to deal with the snow. If you travel you best carry food and water for emergency and tools to dig your car out!...
